task.summary: Added method to calculate point on edge at given distance from start of edge.
Implemented algorithm for calculating carrot path
Improved mouse listener to allow easier path drawing.
Added option to lock robot position
Fixed bug when both angles was equal to zero
Added Mover2D and Robot class and supporting classes Point and Vector.
Added orientation to robot and updated code with new classes.
Refactored a lot of vertices to points
Movement of robot can now be simulated.
